"{\"uid\": \"velo.outsideonline.com-olympics-how-to-watch-cycling-during-the-2024-summer-olympics-in-paris-france\", \"text\": \"Powered byOutside  IZU, JAPAN - AUGUST 03: Chloe Dygert, Megan Jastrab, Jennifer Valente, Emma White of Team United States sprint during the Women's team pursuit finals, bronze medal of the Track Cycling on day eleven of the Tokyo 2020 Olympic Games at Izu Velodrome on August 03, 2021 in Izu, Japan. (Photo by Justin Setterfield/Getty Images)  The 2024 Summer Olympics kick off Friday, July 26 in Paris, France. There are five cycling disciplines at this year's Olympics - road, mountain, track, BMX freestyle, and BMX racing - and a cycling event to watch every single day of the Games. There will be 22 events across the five disciplines.    Both the men's and women's time trials kick off the Olympic cycling events on Saturday, July 27, followed by cross-country mountain biking on Sunday and Monday. The men's and women's road races follow one week later.  Read also:These are the cyclists Team USA is sending to the Olympics  The cycling events of the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris are scheduled to run at four different venues: Pont d'I\\u00e9na for road and time trial races; V\\u00e9lodrome de Saint-Quentin-en-Yvelines for track cycling and BMX racing; \\u00c9lancourt Hill for mountain biking; and Place de la Concorde for the BMX freestyle.  In the United States, the Olympics will beshown on TV on NBCandstreamed on Peacock. We have put together a calendar of when each event will shown; the full streaming schedule of all cycling events can be foundhere.  8:30 AM ET-Women's Individual Time Trial  10:24 AM ET - Men's Individual Time Trial  8:00 AM ET - Women's Cross-Country  8:00 AM ET - Men's Cross-Country  7:30 AM ET - BMX Freestyle Women's Park Seeding  9:18 AM ET - BMX Freestyle Men's Park Seeding  7:10 AM ET -\\u00a0 BMX Freestyle Women's Park Finals  8:50 AM ET - BMX Freestyle Men's Park Finals  2:00 PM ET - BMX Racing Men's and Women's Quarters (3 Rounds)  4:05 PM ET - BMX Racing Men's and Women's Last Chance Qualifiers  2:00 PM ET - BMX Racing Men's and Women's Semi-Finals (3 Rounds)  3:35 PM ET - BMX Racing Men's and Women's Finals  5:00 AM ET - Men's Road Race  8:00 AM ET - Women's Road Race  11:00 AM ET -Women's Team Sprint Qualifying  Men's Team Pursuit Qualifying  Women's Team Sprint First Round  Men's Team Sprint Qualifying  Women's Team Sprint Finals  11:30 AM ET -Women's Team Pursuit Qualifying  Men's Team Sprint First Round  Men's Team Pursuit First Round  Mens Team Sprint Finals  6:45 AM ET -Men's Sprint Qualifying  Women's Keirin First Round  Women's Team Pursuit First Round  Men's Sprint 1/32 Finals  Women's Keirin Repechages  Men's Sprint 1/32 Finals Repechages  11:30 AM ET -Men's Sprint 1/16 Finals  Men's Team Pursuit Finals  Men's Sprint 1/16 Finals Repechages  Women's Team Pursuit Finals  Men's Sprint 1/8 Finals  Men's Sprint 1/8 Finals Repechages  11:00 AM ET -Men's Omnium Scratch Race 1/4  Women's Keirin Quarterfinals  Men's Omnium Tempo Race 2/4  Men's Sprint Quarterfinals  Women's Keirin Semifinals  Men's Omnium Elimination Race 3/4  Women's Keirin Finals  Men's Omnium Points Race 4/4  Men's Sprint Race for 5th-8th Places  8:00 AM ET -Women's Sprint Qualifying  Men's Sprint Semifinals  Women's Sprint 1/32 Finals  Women's Sprint 1/32 Finals Repechages  12:00 PM ET -Women's Madison Final  Women's Sprint 1/16 Finals  Men's Sprint Final  Women's Sprint 1/16 Finals Repechages  11:00 AM ET -Women's Sprint 1/8 Finals  Men's Keirin First Round  Women's Sprint 1/8 Finals Repechages  Men's Madison Final  Women's Sprint Quarterfinals  Men's Keirin Repechages  5:00 AM ET -Women's Omnium Scratch Race 1/4  Women's Sprint Semifinals  Men's Keirin Quarterfinals  Women's Omnium Tempo Race 214  Women's Sprint Race for 5th-8th Places  Men's Keirin Semifinals  Women's Sprint Finals  Women's Omnium Elimination Race 3/4  Men's Keirin Finals  Women's Omnium Points Race 4/4\"}"